bibdata.title: Troubleshooting - Indexmanager will get stuck if previous_to_full_incremental dump causes errors

comments.body:
The specific case in bibdata_staging was that the specific incremental dump has attached dumpfiles but the files do not exist in the vm. In this case it would be better to remove the specific record from the database so that it doesn't blow up the process and trigger a 'General Publishing job' in alma so that you will run a full reindex in the next days.
Second option would be if you have the exact file you can always move it on the server. In the next retry it will see it and index it.
Add this in the docs.

Changes that were made in the alma sandbox came through in bibdata-staging and were indexed. Latest incremental that was triggered in Alma, created event/dump with id 684 in bibdata-staging. 
The event that was logged in AWS from this Alma job is: https://console.aws.amazon.com/cloudwatch/home?region=us-east-1#logsV2:log-groups/log-group/$252Faws$252Flambda$252Falma-webhook-monitor-staging-WebhookReceiver-za2o0tUQ0XNM/log-events/2022$252F01$252F25$252F$255B$2524LATEST$255D62f4a9779bcf41a7b3f81b1f0f82869e

dspace-development.title: Ensure that submitted OAR Items with the workflow state for "Needs Review" be advanced to "Review" where necessary

comments.body:
The following is successfully updating the workflow state for the affected Items:

```bash
/dspace/bin/dspace dsrun edu.princeton.oar.Archive --eperson 'jrg5@princeton.edu' --select 'dc.rights' --value 'Final published version. This is an open access article.' --provenance_msg 'archive_without_email' --workflow_state reviewed --new_workflow_state archive_without_email --verbose
```

The following records must be updated manually, but this should soon be resolved:

```bash
                                             text_value                                             | workflow_id | resource_id
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+-------------+-------------
 Final published version. This is an open access article.                                           |        2453 |        2553
 Final published version. Article is made available in OAR by the publisher's permission or policy. |        2661 |        2761
 Final published version. Article is made available in OAR by the publisher's permission or policy. |        2662 |        2762
 Final published version. Article is made available in OAR by the publisher's permission or policy. |       10604 |       10475
 Final published version. Article is made available in OAR by the publisher's permission or policy. |       14453 |        4915
 Final published version. Article is made available in OAR by the publisher's permission or policy. |       14941 |       14580

(7 rows)
```
The workflow state for these Items have been updated, and this should be prepared for review.
